00:00:01,600 --> 00:00:03,674
The Little Prince
《小王子》

2
00:00:12,554 --> 00:00:15,977
One day, the engine on my plane broke down,
一天   我的飞机引擎坏了

3
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:18,628
and I was forced to land in a desert.
只好迫降在沙漠

4
00:00:20,314 --> 00:00:22,445
There was a severe sandstorm
沙漠刮起了很大的沙尘暴

5
00:00:22,485 --> 00:00:25,445
and though I tried my hardest to get the engine fixed,
尽管我想尽办法想修复引擎

6
00:00:25,491 --> 00:00:27,531
the plane wouldn't start.
飞机仍无法发动

7
00:00:29,508 --> 00:00:33,217
